12. Go to transaction /IWFND/MAINT\_SERVICE and click Add Service

## Activate in Gateway Client (/IWFND/GW\_CLIENT)

15.  Go to the SAP Gateway Client /IWFND/GW\_CLIENT  
16. Enter the URL for the service:  
    /sap/opu/odata/sap/Z\_BW\_ODATA\_0FI\_AR\_4\_1\_SRV/?$format=xml  
     and click execute.
